# Microsoft.Agents.AI & Microsoft.Extensions.AI API Surface

## Package Versions
- **Microsoft.Agents.AI**: 1.0.0
- **Microsoft.Extensions.AI**: 10.4.0 (also 9.10.2 available)

---

## AGENT CREATION & CONFIGURATION

### 1. Create an Agent: `ChatClientAgent`
```csharp
// Constructor Options (choose one):

// Option 1: Full constructor with inline parameters
new ChatClientAgent(
    IChatClient chatClient,
    string instructions,
    string name,
    string description,
    IList<AITool> tools,
    ILoggerFactory loggerFactory,
    IServiceProvider services
)

// Option 2: Using ChatClientAgentOptions  
new ChatClientAgent(
    IChatClient chatClient,
    ChatClientAgentOptions options,
    ILoggerFactory loggerFactory,
    IServiceProvider services
)
```

### 2. Agent Configuration Class: `ChatClientAgentOptions`
```csharp
class ChatClientAgentOptions
{
    string Id { get; set; }
    string Name { get; set; }
    string Description { get; set; }

    // Chat configuration
    ChatOptions ChatOptions { get; set; }

    // History management
    ChatHistoryProvider ChatHistoryProvider { get; set; }

    // Context providers
    IEnumerable<AIContextProvider> AIContextProviders { get; set; }

    // Behavior flags
